narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Although it was a lot of work, I think JAPN 150 was a very helpful course, and I would recommend it to anyone who really wishes to improve their Japanese.
Yes, I would recommend it. But I would say that they should be prepared for a fairly intense workload.
